THIRD-PARTY ATTRIBUTION

Parts of this package are independent Julia reimplementations of algorithms from
the following BSD-licensed MATLAB toolboxes.  No source code from these toolboxes
is vendored into this repository; the directional filter bank (DFB) and
nonsubsampled DFB, the "pkva" ladder filters, and the resampling / separable
filtering helpers are ported from their published algorithms and function
descriptions, so the original copyright and disclaimer are retained below as
required by the BSD license.

* MATLAB Contourlet Toolbox
  Copyright (c) Minh N. Do.
  https://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/8837-contourlet-toolbox

* MATLAB Nonsubsampled Contourlet Toolbox
  Copyright (c) Arthur L. da Cunha, Jianping Zhou, and Minh N. Do.
  https://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/10049-nonsubsampled-contourlet-toolbox

Both toolboxes are distributed under the BSD license:

  Redistribution and use in source and binary forms, with or without
  modification, are permitted provided that the above copyright notice and this
  list of conditions are retained.  THIS SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED BY THE COPYRIGHT
  HOLDERS "AS IS" AND ANY EXPRESS OR IMPLIED WARRANTIES ARE DISCLAIMED.
